WEBVTT

00:10:28.160 --> 00:10:33.176
Hindu fundamentalists today
view this murderer as a national hero,

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:37.016
and they want to put up
statues of him throughout India.

00:10:37.040 --> 00:10:38.656
They've been involved for decades

00:10:38.680 --> 00:10:41.216
in large-scale mass violence
against minorities.

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:43.856
They ban books, art, films.

00:10:43.880 --> 00:10:46.136
They attack romantic couples
on Valentine's Day,

00:10:46.160 --> 00:10:48.216
Christians on Christmas Day.

00:10:48.240 --> 00:10:51.136
They don't like others talking critically

00:10:51.160 --> 00:10:53.776
about what they see
as their ancient culture

00:10:53.800 --> 00:10:55.296
or using its images

00:10:55.320 --> 00:10:56.936
or caricaturing it

00:10:56.960 --> 00:10:59.520
or drawing cartoons about it.